---
title: Pork Schnitzel & Cheesy Garlic Sauce with Roasted Rosemary Potatoes
description: We've turbo-charged schnitzel night! Special additions like a too-good-to-be-true cheesy garlic sauce, rosemary on the golden
chunks of potato and a robust salad are what it's all about. Happy days indeed!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-schnitzel-cheesy-garlic-sauce-c5a81615.jpg
